{"tid":1971503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西機場偷200萬件醫療物資 巴西上海同鄉會長遭逮捕","createTime":"2020-04-14T03:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T00:38:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"35d7b7e699bf3307ccd9d2f9ce8c173ec4f10cd1","tid":1971503,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://politica.estadao.com.br/blogs/fausto-macedo/wp-content/uploads/sites/41/3000/10/zheng-2_130420205844.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolitica.estadao.com.br%2Fblogs%2Ffausto-macedo%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F41%2F3000%2F10%2Fzheng-2_130420205844.png&h=b25cf93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://politica.estadao.com.br/blogs/fausto-macedo/a-prisao-do-homem-que-promove-laco-de-amizade-entre-o-brasil-e-a-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolitica.estadao.com.br%2Fblogs%2Ffausto-macedo%2Fa-prisao-do-homem-que-promove-laco-de-amizade-entre-o-brasil-e-a-china%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B82WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=933e9a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://politica.estadao.com.br/blogs/fausto-macedo/a-prisao-do-homem-que-promove-laco-de-amizade-entre-o-brasil-e-a-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020-04-14 10:03:07<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕巴西警方11日逮捕了10名中國人，其中帶頭的是擔任巴西上海同鄉總會會長的鄭小雲，這些人竊取巴西對抗武漢肺炎的200萬件醫療物資，包括口罩、手套、帽子、工作服、酒精凝膠、溫度計，以及15000個武漢肺炎病毒的檢測試劑盒。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，在巴西瓜魯柳斯（Guarulhos）的昆畢卡國際機場（Cumbica airport）9日發生竊盜案，包括200萬件醫療物資和15000個武漢肺炎病毒的檢測試劑盒遭竊，價值約為400萬雷亞爾（約新台幣2248萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n警方接獲線報後，11日突擊搜查上海同鄉總會，發現數千項病毒測試盒和數百萬套防護配備，大部分貨品與昆畢卡國際機場遭竊的醫療物資相匹配。帶頭者是來自中國的鄭小雲（Zheng Xiao Yun），他擔任上海同鄉總會會長。<br />\n<br />\n鄭小雲向警方供稱，倉庫中的貨物是來自商人的捐贈，將被轉移給巴西的醫院使用，但警方不信鄭小雲的說詞，將這些人逮捕；鄭小雲的說詞也未能說服巴西公共事務部和司法部，他被裁定無限期監禁。<br />\n<br />\n警方後來表示，這些被偷的醫療資源是巴西幾家私立醫院的訂單，卻在昆畢卡國際機場被竊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3132729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3132729&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B82WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=5ce3486a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3132729&h=fdf97069\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3132729</a>"},{"pid":"2491b7c46337891df07d3a566d7f41481525f10d","tid":1971503,"uid":194326,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"小雲同物資好重要"},{"pid":"0b0b02ead882a7b079b2efb72bd20251c155fdcc","tid":1971503,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等口交部幫手"},{"pid":"7ad622585121f607ac6c266437ac472c6c0e5eb8","tid":1971503,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"交佢比巴西黑幫私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa4e663834bde9ec177c9b99bb5b2df4ead61f4","tid":1971503,"uid":4719,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"我有本事自己拎到點解要我還！"},{"pid":"1bc61806de1b1728e413373e5807ff28ded3869d","tid":1971503,"uid":77277,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ad622585121f607ac6c266437ac472c6c0e5eb8","tid":1971503,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"交佢比巴西黑幫私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"就地正法"},{"pid":"3348bf6f6ddfd35b2149ad8669d9a2362780cd9c","tid":1971503,"uid":212509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"無限期監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4bc27e661abe80d49777217d2129414c061a5d","tid":1971503,"uid"